      <p>Travelers are advised to stay informed about weather forecasts, heed local authorities' guidance, and have a contingency plan in case of severe weather. By staying vigilant and prepared, visitors can ensure their safety and contribute to the resilience of the communities they visit, even in the face of unpredictable hurricane activity.</p>
